      "content": "it's not just a \"break\" though. its like the spark is gone for good. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just this biological machine that exists to eat and sleep. if the art was the only thing that made me real, then what am i actually doing here? it feels like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me.",
