    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"new interest.\" there's no \"finding myself\" in something else. the core is just dead. it's like a house where the foundation crumbled and now there's just the empty walls standing there, looking pathetic. if the soul of the person is the art, and the art is dead, then the house is just a ruin. why keep the walls standing when there's nothing inside to keep warm?",
      "source": "evaluator"
